name: Opposites Attract
description:
Two Eastern Grey Squirrels - one melanistic and one not - play together and cuddle on a tree trunk in the dappled sunlight. (Sciurus carolinensis) 

2018. Nikon D60, 55-200mm Lens.

Photographed in situ, without the use of artificial lighting or staging. Photoshop only used for resizing.

1024x685 300dpi jpeg
